OL,3,CBoy, 12, charged after alleged sexual
OL,4,Cassault on woman in her 60s
OL,6,FA 12-year-old boy has been charged
OL,7,Fafter a woman was found with serious
OL,8,Finjuries in Birmingham.
OL,10,FA woman in her 60s remains in a
OL,11,Fserious condition in hospital, after
OL,12,Fshe was discovered in Kellett Road
OL,13,Fjust before 6.15pm on Wednesday 18
OL,14,FMarch.
OL,16,FThe boy was arrested and has been
OL,17,Fcharged with wounding and sexual
OL,18,Fassault.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
