OL,3,CBoy, 12, charged after alleged sexual
OL,4,Cassault on woman in her 60s
OL,6,FHe's also been charged with a separate
OL,7,Ftheft matter last Wednesday and
OL,8,Fintentional strangulation after a
OL,9,Fwoman was confronted in the street
OL,10,Flast month.
OL,12,FThe boy, who cannot be named due to
OL,13,Fhis age, is remanded to appear before
OL,14,FBirmingham Youth Court today
OL,15,F(Wednesday 24 March).
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
