OL,3,CBoy, 12, charged after alleged sexual
OL,4,Cassault on woman in her 60s
OL,6,FWest Midlands Police said: "Our
OL,7,Fenquiries remain ongoing, but we
OL,8,Funderstand how concerning this will be
OL,9,Fwithin the community. Our officers
OL,10,Fwill be continuing to provide
OL,11,Freassurance in the local area.
OL,13,F"If anyone has any information
OL,14,Fregarding suspicious behaviour on 18
OL,15,FMarch or in the days leading up to
OL,16,Flast Wednesday, details can be
OL,17,Fsubmitted via the Major Incident
OL,18,FPublic Portal or via 101 quoting log
OL,19,F4888 of 18 March."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
